1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:03,674 --> 00:01:06,874
(Beg Me)

4
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:58,120
Oh, it's Spring Fever
from Zuixian Building.

5
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,319
Everyone, kill him!

6
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,960
Save me, dear!

7
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,520
What are you doing here?

8
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,560
Who exactly are you?

9
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:41,000
Sorry, I'm drugged with Spring Fever.

10
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,639
Spring Fever?

11
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:45,439
Why were you given Spring Fever?

12
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,400
And why are you here?

13
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:50,800
After you left, assassins came.

14
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,319
Xuan Qing was beaten.

15
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,919
Xuan Qing, how is she?

16
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:59,439
I lured the assassins away. She's fine.

17
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:05,360
Spring Fever is the strongest love drug
at Zuixian Building.

18
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:07,240
Specifically used to tame resistant men.

19
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,240
Don't you know

20
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:13,919
cold water intensifies its effects?

21
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,879
What should be done then?

22
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:36,959
Beg me.

23
00:04:43,002 --> 00:04:47,296
♪Because my heart
knew you at first sight♪

24
00:04:48,903 --> 00:04:54,354
♪I want to hold tight
this love on the wind♪

25
00:04:55,872 --> 00:05:01,344
♪Even if it's just fleeting joy♪

26
00:05:01,786 --> 00:05:07,808
♪It can become a memory I'll hold onto♪

27
00:05:09,018 --> 00:05:13,643
♪If halfway through, you leave me♪

28
00:05:15,305 --> 00:05:20,517
♪I'd still welcome another storm♪

29
00:05:22,257 --> 00:05:27,512
♪Our stolen moment passes too soon♪

30
00:05:28,048 --> 00:05:34,661
♪Unable to wait for this love to bloom♪

31
00:05:36,352 --> 00:05:38,592
♪Who isn't just a passerby♪

32
00:05:38,592 --> 00:05:41,312
♪And whose only one are you♪

33
00:05:41,594 --> 00:05:42,944
♪Who broke♪

34
00:05:43,258 --> 00:05:44,688
♪Whose heart♪

35
00:05:44,858 --> 00:05:47,284
♪Yet find it hard to part♪

36
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:51,463
♪Trapped in pain's shallows♪

37
00:05:51,648 --> 00:05:54,432
♪Letting tears run wild♪

38
00:05:54,778 --> 00:05:57,152
♪Only then realizing your hand♪

39
00:05:57,152 --> 00:06:01,180
♪Holds my thread♪

40
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,000
Master.

41
00:06:16,279 --> 00:06:17,680
What exactly happened?

42
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:20,480
Assassins attacked today.

43
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,600
Master Zhaoxi is...

44
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,600
Just drugged.

45
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:36,240
Have you found out
the assassins' origins?

46
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,000
They tried to conceal their moves.

47
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:43,920
But their fighting style
strongly suggests the Xuanji Pavilion.

48
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,000
It seems we won't get
anything out of him today.

49
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:00,199
Enough.

50
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,959
Let's go ask his old mother instead.

51
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:08,680
She might be willing
to tell us something.

52
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:14,360
Where is she? What did you do to her?

53
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,639
She's fine for now.

54
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:20,000
Whether she remains
fine later is unknown.

55
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,279
It was Master Chaosheng.

56
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,720
Zuixian Building's owner is dead.

57
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:43,399
Master, if Master Chaosheng
is behind all this,

58
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,399
will you really...?

59
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:48,319
Whether it was him or not
makes no difference.

60
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:53,000
Since there's irrefutable proof
he hired the assassin,

61
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:56,000
I will make sure he pays the price.

62
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,839
But the family head...

63
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,920
The young Gus are still around.

64
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:11,000
Why do you think they let
an outsider like me interfere?

65
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,519
I don't know.

66
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:19,560
Others call Chaosheng mister.

67
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:25,720
Only Xuanji Pavilion members
call him master.

68
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,080
You're awake.

69
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,440
Where's Madam?

70
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,440
Prince Rui invites several Gus
to his banquet at Zuixian Building.

71
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:05,320
She said you needn't attend. Rest well.

72
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,519
She'll be back soon.

73
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:13,919
Yesterday, you drew the assassins away?

74
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,240
Of course.

75
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,960
What? Are you doubting me?

76
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:35,519
Wine's unavoidable at a banquet.
I'll brew her a sobering soup later.

77
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:52,120
I didn't expect you to know such things.

78
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,720
Why wouldn't I?

79
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:59,639
Scholars can't touch a cooking pot?

80
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:03,519
I just didn't think you were the type.

81
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,279
The soup is ready.

82
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:30,399
Remember to give it
to my wife when she returns.

83
00:10:30,746 --> 00:10:36,410
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

84
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,840
I'm going out. Are you going with me?

85
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:44,659
Where to?

86
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:05,056
(Zuixian Building)

87
00:11:05,056 --> 00:11:06,066
Sit anywhere.

88
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,159
Will Yuluo come today?

89
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,799
If she weren't coming today,

90
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:24,080
would you have even bothered
to come back and see me?

91
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:30,200
Is the one in the Fufeng Pavilion
truly my brother?

92
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,519
Whether it is or isn't,

93
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:36,120
since it involves murder,
the authorities will decide.

94
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,960
This is Xuanji's place after all.
Be careful. Walls have ears.

95
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:48,320
The long-vanished Tianji Sect
once had five disciples.

96
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:51,480
The eldest, Chang Qi,
followed by Yun Sui,

97
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:54,519
Gu Jiang, Qin Yuheng,

98
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,120
and the youngest, Lianyi.

99
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,639
Later, Qin Yuheng
became Left Chancellor.

100
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:01,919
Lianyi, as a general's daughter,
married into the palace.

101
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,759
Yun Sui founded the Xuanji Pavilion.

102
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:07,080
Gu Jiang became a merchant.

103
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,600
Later, Qin Yuheng's entire family
was massacred.

104
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:14,960
Chang Qi vanished without a trace.
Yun Sui married Gu Jiang

105
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:18,120
and gave birth to our brother Gu Zhaoxi.

106
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,279
But I've heard

107
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:24,879
Yun Sui was already pregnant
before marrying Gu Jiang.

108
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:30,519
Some things are better left unknown.

109
00:12:30,519 --> 00:12:31,600
You just need to know

110
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:33,639
that as long as I'm here,

111
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:37,120
you can always be carefree
as Gu Wenshuang.

112
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:44,399
Let's go. Don't keep Prince Rui waiting.

113
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,480
So Zhaoxi...

114
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:02,000
I never knew Wenshuang
and Chaosheng were this close.

115
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,559
I wonder what scheme
Chaosheng is plotting.

116
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:08,440
Is he genuinely being nice,
or does he want Wenshuang's support?

117
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:12,200
How do you think Chaosheng

118
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,039
learned Zhaoxi isn't truly a Gu?

119
00:13:14,759 --> 00:13:16,799
And how did Wenshuang learn that too?

120
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:21,919
You invited me here
just to show me this?

121
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:23,480
Of course not.

122
00:13:23,879 --> 00:13:26,919
I called you here
to help me choose a dress.

123
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,000
But...

124
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:33,759
if Zhaoxi truly isn't a Gu,
what will you do?

125
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:41,679
I trust you won't easily believe
such groundless rumors.

126
00:13:42,879 --> 00:13:45,200
I understand now.

127
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,080
Let's go.

128
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:49,279
Since Prince Rui invited us,
we shouldn't keep him waiting.

129
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:53,039
But, why would Prince Rui
suddenly host a banquet?

130
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:04,960
It's truly an honor
to have you all here.

131
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,879
Make yourselves at home.

132
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:10,039
Chaosheng and I
have been friends through art.

133
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:13,559
Xuanji has graciously cared
for the ladies I've befriended.

134
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,919
As for Wenshuang,
I've watched him grow up.

135
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:22,399
And your third brother

136
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:23,879
isn't here today,

137
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:25,759
but since I'm close with Chaosheng,

138
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:29,840
I'll regard you as my sister-in-law.

139
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:33,440
I'm unworthy.

140
00:14:35,559 --> 00:14:36,720
Just a pity

141
00:14:37,279 --> 00:14:41,080
that I obtained an unfinished chess game
and heard that Zhaoxi excels at chess.

142
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,519
I wanted to challenge him.

143
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,960
Now, it seems my wish
may go unfulfilled.

144
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,360
What's so difficult?

145
00:14:48,799 --> 00:14:51,480
If you're interested,
I'll send someone to go get him.

146
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,039
Your Highness.

147
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,840
I've discussed chess strategies
with my husband many times.

148
00:14:57,919 --> 00:15:02,480
Might I be your opponent, Your Highness?

149
00:15:03,519 --> 00:15:06,679
I can't refuse
an invitation from a beauty.

150
00:15:07,679 --> 00:15:08,320
Someone!

151
00:15:17,759 --> 00:15:18,320
Your Highness.

152
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:22,240
Sorry.

153
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,080
You seem troubled.

154
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:32,679
Bandits were just subdued,
but heavy rains outside the city

155
00:15:32,879 --> 00:15:35,279
caused landslides
that destroyed the Yunya Temple.

156
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:38,320
My father fell gravely ill
over my brother's incident.

157
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:40,159
I never wanted to interfere,

158
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:43,159
but now, I realize my own helplessness.

159
00:15:45,159 --> 00:15:48,320
Given a choice,
I'd rather be a simple prince,

160
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:51,840
spending my days in chess
and art in a peaceful world.

161
00:15:53,799 --> 00:15:57,159
It's rare to have all of you here.
Let's speak no more of this. Continue.

162
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:03,200
Your Highness.

163
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:12,559
Something's come up at home.
Please enjoy yourselves.

164
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,320
Wenshuang, care for a game?

165
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,120
Pity this game remains unfinished.

166
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:48,519
But why didn't you conceal your skill

167
00:16:48,679 --> 00:16:50,360
when playing against Prince Rui?

168
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:53,720
Weren't you afraid
he'd blame you if he lost?

169
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,600
Prince Rui played masterfully,

170
00:16:57,039 --> 00:17:00,840
appearing casual
while calculating every move.

171
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:03,320
Would you lose this game?

172
00:17:04,759 --> 00:17:07,119
It's too early to tell.

173
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:10,000
Chess reveals the mind indeed.

174
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:12,400
Have you ever met a player
you couldn't see through?

175
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,359
Could it be Zhaoxi?

176
00:17:48,762 --> 00:17:55,559
(Zuixian Building)

177
00:17:55,559 --> 00:17:58,119
Yuluo, that day, I...

178
00:18:01,319 --> 00:18:02,119
I'm sorry.

179
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:05,440
Can we return to how we were before?

180
00:18:06,039 --> 00:18:07,720
We've known each other for five years.

181
00:18:08,119 --> 00:18:10,880
At the Xuanji Pavilion,
you never acted like a young master.

182
00:18:11,519 --> 00:18:13,200
You were kind and passionate,

183
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:17,440
the purest soul I've ever known.

184
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:20,960
To me, you were more than
just a fellow disciple.

185
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:23,440
Young Master.

186
00:18:24,559 --> 00:18:26,880
I genuinely considered you my brother.

187
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:31,680
Now, I'm married to Zhaoxi,
and I call you Wenshuang like he does.

188
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:35,799
I naturally won't hold
your careless words that day against you.

189
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:42,440
It's getting late. I must return.
You should return too.

190
00:19:43,994 --> 00:19:49,057
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

191
00:19:49,594 --> 00:19:54,915
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

192
00:19:55,482 --> 00:20:02,110
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

193
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:06,874
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

194
00:20:06,874 --> 00:20:09,210
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

195
00:20:09,210 --> 00:20:15,910
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

196
00:20:15,910 --> 00:20:22,682
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

197
00:20:22,682 --> 00:20:29,818
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

198
00:20:29,818 --> 00:20:34,202
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

199
00:20:34,202 --> 00:20:36,826
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

200
00:20:36,826 --> 00:20:43,460
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

201
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:50,010
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

202
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:57,134
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

203
00:20:57,224 --> 00:21:01,594
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

204
00:21:01,594 --> 00:21:04,302
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

205
00:21:04,302 --> 00:21:10,202
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

206
00:21:10,842 --> 00:21:16,830
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
